#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds MMA martial arts support for weapons from various mods <color_light_red>NOTE, you MUST have the mods below enabled, otherwise it will throw a NEGLIGIBLE (ignorable) error</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_green>Currently supported mods: Magiclysm, BL9, Cata++, Battle Maid, CBM Equipment, Really Dark Skies, Ninja_Mod, Project Kawaii, Nechronica Redux, vorpal weapons, The Vermilion Mod</color>"
msgstr ""
"为来自多个模组的武器添加MMA武术支持<color_light_red>注意，你必须启用以下模组，否则会抛出一个可忽略（可无视）的错误</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_green>当前支持的模组：Magiclysm、BL9、Cata++、Battle Maid、CBM Equipment、Really Dark Skies、Ninja_Mod、Project Kawaii、Nechronica Redux、vorpal weapons、The Vermilion Mod</color>"
